1. Mi *planiramo* da posetimo Beograd sledećeg vikenda. (We are planning to visit Belgrade next weekend.)
2. Oni su *planirali* da kupe novi automobil, ali su odustali. (They had planned to buy a new car, but they changed their minds.)
3. Kada *planiraš* da završiš svoj diplomski rad? (When are you planning to finish your master's thesis?)
4. Njihov *planirani* put na more je odložen zbog lošeg vremena. (Their planned trip to the seaside was postponed due to bad weather.)
5. Ona je već *planirala* svoj godišnji odmor i neće moći da promeni datume. (She has already planned her vacation and won't be able to change the dates.)
6. Da li si *planirao* šta ćeš raditi za vikend? (Did you plan what you'll do this weekend?)
7. Tokom pandemije, mnogi događaji su bili *planirani* da se održe onlajn. (During the pandemic, many events were planned to take place online.)
8. *Planirajte* unapred i izbegnite stres. (Plan ahead and avoid stress.)
9. Ovaj projekat je *planiran* za realizaciju u narednih godinu dana. (This project is planned for implementation in the next year.)
10. Kako bi uspeli da postignemo svoje ciljeve, moramo *planirati* detaljno. (In order to achieve our goals, we need to plan thoroughly.)